# Project Rules

## Documentation
Architecture rules: `docs/arc-rules.md`
Business requirements: `docs/requirements.md`
Implementation plan: `docs/plan.md`
Current architecture: `docs/architecture.md`
Always read these documents before starting work.

## Architecture Updates
After ANY code changes, update `docs/architecture.md`:
- Add new modules/files
- Describe changes
- Update component relationships

## Working with Tasks
1. Read the task
2. Create a plan (3-5 steps)
3. Wait for confirmation
4. Implement
5. Update architecture.md